response.overview: Short comedy about a man who dreams that he runs over everyone with his skates.  A man falls asleep on the sidewalk and dreams that he gets into trouble with his homemade skates because he runs over everyone. He is woken up with a garden hose by two mischievous boys. When he takes the garden hose away, a police officer gets wet, which puts the man in trouble after all.
response.title: Patins à Roulettes
